ShippingRateBuilder
Example to create an instance using the builder pattern 

     ShippingRate shippingRate = ShippingRate.builder()
             .price(priceBuilder -> priceBuilder)
             .plusTiers(tiersBuilder -> tiersBuilder)
             .build()
